---
title: Sri Lankan Pulled Beef & Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice & Crushed Peanuts
description: This creamy coconut pulled beef curry will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night. It's filled to the brim with
bright veggies and finished with a sprinkling of flair from the crushed peanuts.

*Our pulled beef is gently cooked while vacuum-sealed (or sous vide as the French say). The meat may look pale, but it's packed with flavour and moisture!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-sri-lankan-pulled-beef-veggie-curry-05107bc9.jpg
